title: Episode 30: The Virtual Psychology Museum
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this episode, we discuss the newly launched Virtual Museum of Psychology (http://psychmuseum.uwgb.org/), brought to you by the UW-Green Bay Psychology Program.  We discuss what it is, why we built it, and how it came to be.  Guests include Kate Farley, Annie Jones, Luke Konkol, Allee Schramm, and Annemarie Schwery.
